quote.summary: National United Resources Holdings Ltd is an investment holding company principally engaged in the car rental business. The Company operates its business through two segments. The Car Rental and Shuttle Bus business segment is mainly engaged in the provision of shuttle services between workplaces/schools and residential communities for employees/students of institutional customers business. The segment also engages in providing vehicle rental without chauffeur. The segment also engages in the provision of car rental with chauffeur for business and leisure travel and large government events. The Information Technology Business segment is mainly engaged in the provision of cloud computing, global traffic operations and digital transformation services via privately owned constructed data analytics infrastructure with system application software of computational analytics and processing center. The segment also engages in research and development, production, sales and services of industry
